{"type":"message","id":"6cd53abd","parentId":"b352ea52","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:20:11.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me summarize what I did.","thinkingSignature":"e321f7d7eb1f5a18a8f2a097234a94f0ddf67493fd75ccfa16356c0f565f5c64"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n✅ **自主学习完成**（无活跃对话触发）\n\n已保存到 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`，整理了3个方向的行业关键信息：\n\n1. **企业数字化转型**：国家数字经济创新型企业培育政策、工业数据筑基行动、北京/广东量化目标\n2. **智能安防与弱电工程**：市场规模（2026年智能安防7800亿→2030年1.4万亿）、AIoT技术趋势、民用化扩张\n3. **IT运维与网络集成**：Agentic AIOps智能自治运维、云原生多云管理、NaaS普及、ITIL深度落地\n\n同时梳理了对道简网络的4点启示，涵盖数字化转型商机、智能安防民用市场、运维智能化升级、网络集成等方向。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4906,"output":181,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49068,"cost":{"input":0.0014717999999999999,"output":0.0002172,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00300843}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775078406097}}
